Author: NutellaLicka#4241
Content: @CiPhEr no there is not. The decision to choose a pool is completely personal. People need to inform themselves of which one would best suit their needs. Pirate has multiple pools, all with slightly different features and websites. I implore people to do a bit of research and look into all the pools and what they offer before making a decision. It seems as though the single pool with most of the hash gained a lot of popularity through early marketing when it was the only pool, and people are not interested in switching (for various reasons).
